  "title": "Architectural Coordinator (HDB/Condo/Landed Projects)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Oversee on-site architectural works, ensuring quality, accuracy, and timely progress for HDB, condominium, and landed projects.</li><li>Coordinate quotations, material selections, and deliveries, ensuring designs reflect on-site conditions and client/consultant updates.</li><li>Cross-check architectural drawings with structural and M&E plans, resolve discrepancies, and prepare clarification sketches when required.</li><li>Supervise trades, monitor construction sequencing, and hold regular meetings to track progress and ensure smooth project execution.</li></ul><p>Requirements:</p><p><p><ul><li>Diploma in Architecture, Building Technology, Interior Design, or related field closely related <strong>built-environment discipline</strong>.</li><li>At least 3 years’ experience in architectural coordination, site supervision, or construction delivery for <strong>HDB, Condo or Landed Projects</strong>.</li><li>Strong ability to interpret construction drawings, specifications, and on-site technical requirements.</li><li>Proficient in <strong>AutoCAD and Revit</strong>, with excellent organizational, communication, and teamwork skills.</li><li>Knowledge of construction materials, methods, and local building regulations.</li></ul></p></p><p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in <strong>MS Word</strong> to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p><p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p><p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p><p>Registration: R21100996</p>",
